<title>USA: Kulicke &amp; Soffa plans share offering.</title>
<headline>Kulicke &amp; Soffa plans share offering.</headline>
<dateline>WILLOW GROVE, Pa 1997-02-20</dateline>
<text>
<p>Kulicke &amp; Soffa Industries Inc said it intends to soon file a registration statement with the Securities and Exchange Commission for a public offering of approximately three million shares of common stock, plus an over-allotment option of up to 450,000 additional shares.</p>
<p>All of the shares will be offered by the company, which said proceeds will be used to reduce debt and for general corporate purposes.</p>
<p>((--New York Newsdesk, 212/859-1700))</p>
